            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>港股午後偏軟，惟百度<a class=\"color_mpf\" href=\"stock1.php?code=9988\"><strong>（9988）</strong></a>一枝獨秀，曾高見124.8元，急升7.8%，現報121.8元，升幅收窄至5.2%，暫成交17.77億元。</font></p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>近日多間投行發表報告，稱</font>看好<font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>百度</font>AI相關業務增長；此外，路透引述消息報道，百度旗下人工智能晶片子公司昆侖芯考慮香港上市，最快明年第一季向港交所提交上市申請。</p><p>昆侖芯近期完成一輪融資，最新估值達210億元人民幣。</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h2><br/> </h2><p>5.2</p> </div></div>\n</div>",
